OL,3,CAll you need to know about major 12
OL,4,Cmonth roundabout closure
OL,6,FITV News correspondent Mel Barham
OL,7,Fexplains what the closure will mean to
OL,8,Fthe local area
OL,10,FA major roundabout is closing for a
OL,11,Ffull year as work begins on
OL,12,Freconstructing a bridge underneath it.
OL,14,FThe Greek Street roundabout in
OL,15,FStockport is a key thoroughfare
OL,16,Fthrough the town, close to the train
OL,17,Fstation sits above the West Coast
OL,18,Fmainline.
