OL,3,CAll you need to know about major 12
OL,4,Cmonth roundabout closure
OL,6,FThe bridge has come to the end of its
OL,7,Flife and needs replacing, meaning the
OL,8,Froundabout and surrounding roads will
OL,9,Fbe closed for 12 months whilst the
OL,10,Fcomplex project is undertaken.
OL,12,FHere's all you need to know.
OL,14,FWhy are they closing Greek street
OL,15,Froundabout?
OL,17,FThe roundabout, which is actually a
OL,18,Fbridge over the West Coast Mainline,
OL,19,Fwas constructed in 1958, and has
OL,20,Freached the end of its life and needs
OL,21,Freplacing.
