OL,3,CAll you need to know about major 12
OL,4,Cmonth roundabout closure
OL,6,FThe year-long closure is part of
OL,7,FNetwork Rail's almost #20 million
OL,8,Finvestment to replace the aging bridge
OL,9,Fover the Manchester branch of the West
OL,10,FCoast Main Line, Europe's busiest
OL,11,Fmixed-use railway.
OL,13,FWhen will the roundabout be closed and
OL,14,Ffor how long?
OL,16,FThe Greek Street roundabout will close
OL,17,Fon 31 March 2025 for 12 months.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/8
