OL,3,CAll you need to know about major 12
OL,4,Cmonth roundabout closure
OL,6,FVarious roads around the roundabout
OL,7,Fwill be affected including Greek
OL,8,FStreet, King Street West, Mercian Way,
OL,9,Fand Shaw Heath.
OL,11,FPedestrian access will remain open on
OL,12,Fone arm of the roundabout.
OL,14,FYou can find information about
OL,15,Fdiversionary routes here.
OL,17,FWhy will it take so long?
OL,19,FThis is one of the most complex
OL,20,Fstructural engineering projects
OL,21,Fundertaken in Stockport for decades.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/8
