OL,3,CAll you need to know about major 12
OL,4,Cmonth roundabout closure
OL,6,FThe plans involve dismantling the
OL,7,Fexisting bridge in August, using huge
OL,8,Fcranes to lift the 200 concrete bridge
OL,9,Fbeams onto lorries for removal.
OL,11,FThe new bridge beams will then be
OL,12,Finstalled.
OL,14,FThe railway will be closed for 21 days
OL,15,Fwhilst this part of the project takes
OL,16,Fplace.
OL,18,FA scaffold bridge was built over
OL,19,FChristmas 2024 to divert important
OL,20,Futility services.
