OL,3,CAll you need to know about major 12
OL,4,Cmonth roundabout closure
OL,6,FThere will be more railway work
OL,7,Frequired in October and over Christmas
OL,8,F2025.
OL,10,FIn Spring 2026, the work is due to be
OL,11,Fcompleted to reinstate the road over
OL,12,Fthe bridge.
OL,14,FOnce the new bridge is constructed,
OL,15,Fthe roundabouts, pavements and
OL,16,Fsurrounding roads will return to their
OL,17,Foriginal condition and will be ready
OL,18,Fto use again.
OL,20,FHow will it affect me?
