OL,3,CAll you need to know about major 12
OL,4,Cmonth roundabout closure
OL,6,FLocal businesses have voiced concerns
OL,7,Fover the closures, fearing it will
OL,8,Fhave a huge impact on trade.
OL,10,FNetwork Rail say: "We understand
OL,11,Fpeople living in and travelling
OL,12,Fthrough Stockport will be concerned
OL,13,Fabout the road closure.
OL,15,F"Working closely with Stockport
OL,16,FMetropolitan Borough Council and
OL,17,FTransport for Greater Manchester, we
OL,18,Faim to clearly plan and communicate
OL,19,Falternative travel options and
OL,20,Fdiversionary routes. We will share
OL,21,Fthis information as soon as possible.
